Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, close the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure we should leave Perona?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:04:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't take someone we can't find.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh! Where in the world did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.29,0:04:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew! Okay, you can stop now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Lift your invisibility power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.93,0:04:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We're free and clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I was terrified we'd get \Ncaught the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I never did find out what brought\NTyrant Kuma to Thriller Bark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,About that, Absalom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Tyrant Kuma came to tell us the name
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,of the successor to the\Nformer Warlord, Crocodile.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,His successor...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but that's not the important part.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The successor is a man called Blackbeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He's pulled a truly nasty stunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Read that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"Fire Fist Ace, 2nd Division Commander\Nof the Whitebeard Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...has been imprisoned in Impel Down"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:05:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's well known that Ace is\None of Whitebeard's top dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The government just got\Ntheir hands on a powerful card.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Depending on how they play it,\Nthis could completely change the Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got a serious situation on our hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no time for Moria-sama\Nto be dead to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see where you're coming from,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm more interested... in finding a wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Bring me a corpse that turns you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.54,0:05:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want a zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna marry a living woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:38.78,Sign,,0,0,300,,{\blur0.8\fad(0,2600)\fs99\bord2.8\c&H000000&\t(3120,3165,\1a&HFF&)}One day after defeating Moria
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.06,0:05:38.78,Sign,,0,0,300,,{\blur0.8\fad(0,2600)\fs99\bord0\4a&HFF&}One day after defeating Moria
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:34.90,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,In the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:37.52,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,everyone slept all day in that courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:40.89,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Well, sure. We were up all night fighting like mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starving, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibble on some cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheese doesn't cut it!\NCheese doesn't energize me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then start hauling the ingredients\NI need to the courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the members of the Victim\NAssociation don't want to budge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:06:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're eating over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.03,0:06:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.41,0:06:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is just so happy to see\Nthe sun for the first time in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They are crying tears \Nof joy while sunbathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did all of that energy come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so weird! It's a mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have enough food?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.59,0:06:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a mountain of additional food
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,\Non top of everything that was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.09,0:06:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who did that. There are\Nsome nice people out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And they even loaded your ship\Nwith all of this treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.56,0:06:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Even assuming it was Christmas,\Nthis is far too generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bliss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a glass armband!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I claim this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, you know what'll happen\Nif you take any of the treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right, Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He can have it! There aren't any gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is that how this works? Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't have a single\Npiece of treasure for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't take treasure from\Nthe people who saved us, Namizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:06:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a nice knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! This is out. \NIt's studded with gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It popped right out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is Namizo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, this is rather strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,For some odd reason, I don't feel\Nlike this is the first time we've met.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,By any chance, are you Lola?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. Did I tell you my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're Lola!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Lola...? Wh-Whoa, wait! Just a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That boar zombie was her...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.71,0:07:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be confused, huh? \NI'll fill you in later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, take this. It's \Nmy way of thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you sure? You're thanking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami gave away some of our treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going on ahead. Is this everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A storm is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.81,0:07:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A storm? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The light is seeping into my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We're really alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We brought food!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you told us, we would have carried it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,\NWe shouldn't let our savior work!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.72,0:08:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Zoro up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He needs absolute rest, \Nso he's in the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We brought the stuff you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen Zoro so badly hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He nearly lost his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I think something must have happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...while we were unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. I sincerely doubt \Nthat man simply left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's strange how Luffy\Nis bursting with energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:09:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what's up with that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I saw what went down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw what happened from beginning to end!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you the dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fill you in on what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.93,0:09:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! No, wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.31,0:09:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hold up!\N--Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, why?! You were pretty cool yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You were like, "Instead of the\Nswordsman's life, take mine."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now start talking. What happened afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know what happened\Nafter I blacked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That Warlord had yet \Nanother shocking ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.51,0:09:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He pressed his paw against Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It repelled all of the "damage"\Nthat Straw Hat had taken!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,His damage...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.82,0:10:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like a bubble of agony. And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to take his place,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,take all of his pain and \Nsuffering unto yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.87,0:10:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be impossible for you to survive\Nwhen you are already on the brink of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a small taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the swordsman started\Nscreaming bloody murder
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,when he touched a small portion of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to say it, but I \Nthought he was a goner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what makes it so touching!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It seriously made me cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That explains why Luffy is\Ndoing well while Zoro is bedridden.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That was rash!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did all of this blood come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing happened...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Let's tell everyone\Nabout the Straw Hats' heroic story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'm itching to tell them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.06,0:11:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be insensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't risk his life out of\Na desire to earn our gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What would happen if they learned that\NLuffy's pain hurt a friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.70,0:11:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how badly are you \Ndying to tell everyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're killing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All that matters is that everyone is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Let's go eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Th... Th-Th...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys are super cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Their captain is so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So that explains it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you acting like you knew\Nwhat happened? What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask such an insensitive question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All that matters is that everyone is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I wanna tell them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Keep that manly heroic story to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.59,0:12:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Delish! I've never eaten \Nsuch good food before!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.65,0:12:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here! Try this! This!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.65,0:12:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It's been years since\Nwe've eaten a decent meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to be alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.41,0:12:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I cooked up a storm! \NDon't let it go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,To think I get to eat your cooking again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.71,0:13:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This really is lip-smacking good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I have any lips!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to shut up and eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.63,0:13:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That skeleton is hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But honestly--oh, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,After eating until I was full\Nboth yesterday and today,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have gained weight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"Even though I'm a skeleton!"\NI can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.14,0:13:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Skeleton, you rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How come that skeleton is able to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's a hoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a clever skeleton, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you able to move around?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it doesn't really matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,--Oh, dinner!\N--Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,--Dinner!\N--Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,--Dinner!\N--Oh, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,--Dinner!\N--Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,0:13:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,--Dinner!\N--Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.59,0:13:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't have a toast\Nand it still turned into a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's sleeping right through all this noise...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And here he's the toughest guy in the crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chopper! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,--Luffy!\N--This is for Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now drink away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give it to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?! This will fix Zoro\Nright up, since it's his favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What type of treatment is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't work? Then how about meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.89,0:14:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay. I'll gladly accept\Nyour sentiment alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.26,0:14:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But only your sentiment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a piano in this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I thought you only played the violin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can play most instruments.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? You're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I'd like to touch on \Nan earlier conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I also saw what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was greatly moved by what you two did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it wonderful to have comrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't include me in that.\NI merely made a fool of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you bore the same resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to pick a song?\NI'll take a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.16,0:15:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? I can request anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.25,0:15:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:07.45,Shanty ♪,,0,0,0,,Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:11.78,Shanty ♪,,0,0,0,,Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:08.49,Alt,,0,0,0,,Wait, didn't you just ask for a request?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.77,0:16:15.98,Shanty ♪,,0,0,0,,Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.98,0:16:19.95,Shanty ♪,,0,0,0,,Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.36,0:16:24.63,Shanty ♪,,0,0,0,,Time to ship out Binks' Brew!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:26.73,Shanty ♪,,0,0,0,,The sea breeze blows us to who-knows-where,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:28.38,Shanty ♪,,0,0,0,,let the waves be our guide!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:33.08,Shanty ♪,,0,0,0,,O'er across the ocean tide, the sunset stirs, going wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:37.42,Shanty ♪,,0,0,0,,Look to the skies! Watch the circling birds\Nas they sing and pass us by!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:41.74,Shanty ♪,,0,0,0,,Fare thee well to the weaver's town,\Nto the harbor as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:46.00,Shanty ♪,,0,0,0,,Sing a booming song,\Na song for us casting off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:50.21,Shanty ♪,,0,0,0,,Oh, the gold and silver waves,\Nall of 'em turnin' to sea spray!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:54.51,Shanty ♪,,0,0,0,,As we journey off t'ward the ends of the high seas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Binks' Brew." I thought I recognized the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This takes me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.22,0:17:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Whee! Yahoo! Keep it going!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Brook! I know this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shanks and the guys used to sing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. A long time ago,\Nall of the pirates would sing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:18:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They sang it in good times and bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're gonna join our crew now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you've got your shadow back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You can hit the seas without\Nfear of the sun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,About that. There was one thing\NI neglected to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.19,0:18:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised one of my comrades something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I must tend to that first \Nor I will lose face!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You're talking \Nabout Laboon, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know all about it. \NFranky and Robin told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the name of the whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He is at a certain cape--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Brook! We met Laboon\Nat Twin Cape. Honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.39,0:19:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I already knew that Laboon
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,had been waiting there for his friends
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.52,0:19:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to return for the past fifty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Skeleton, what's wrong?\NThe tempo is getting slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the symbol of\Nour promise to fight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Until we come back, don't remove that\Nmark by hitting your head. Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.64,0:19:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya, whale! I'm leaving now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:20:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, was I ever surprised when I learned\Nthat you're the surviving member
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,of the band of pirates he's been waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.34,0:20:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And you still remember your promise to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet Laboon would be thrilled if he knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Just a moment, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm shocked! This is so sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.84,0:20:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true? Did you actually meet Laboon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.84,0:20:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though fifty years have passed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Laboon is still waiting for us at that cape?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling the truth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We also bore witness.\NWe saw him with our own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Was he well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.67,0:20:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure was!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He was as big as a mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.63,0:20:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:21:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When we left him, the cutie \Nwas about the size of a boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a stubborn streak, but he loved music.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a good boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now, I can still...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...picture him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never been this happy in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.60,0:22:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did that whale come from?\NIt's following our ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.70,0:22:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have gotten separated from its pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.74,0:22:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The poor thing. The ocean is a big place!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.41,0:22:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks sad. Well, it's still just a calf.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.59,0:22:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Yorkie, why don't we play a song?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.26,0:22:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Great idea, Brook! Hey, everyone!\NGrab your instruments.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.20,0:22:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's show him what the \NRumbar Pirates that make
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,crying children laugh are made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.83,0:22:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.73,0:22:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.49,0:23:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Laboon, you are our dear comrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.42,0:23:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we can't take you with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grand Line is so dangerous,\Nwe want you to wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.92,0:23:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We will swing around the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.50,0:23:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear we will come back\Nto this cape to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.89,0:23:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.55,0:23:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"Brook's Past\NA Sad Farewell with His Cheerful Comrade"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.01,0:23:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
